ZH: 我昨天收到一个白色的信封。
EN: I received a white envelope yesterday.
ZH: 请把这封信装进这个信封里。
EN: Please put this letter in this envelope.
ZH: 这个信封有你的名字和地址。
EN: This envelope has your name and address.
ZH: 请给我一个大的信封。
EN: Please give me a big envelope.
ZH: 请尽快封好信封。
EN: Please seal the envelope as soon as possible.
ZH: 我找了很久，都没找到这个丢失的信封。
EN: I looked for this lost envelope for a long time but couldn't find it.
ZH: 这个信封的邮票已经过期了。
EN: The stamp on this envelope has already expired.
ZH: 他将一封信放入蓝色的信封中。
EN: He put a letter into a blue envelope.
ZH: 请确保把信放入正确的信封里。
EN: Please make sure to put the letter in the right envelope.
ZH: 这个信封非常美观。
EN: This envelope is very attractive.
ZH: 邮局销售各种类型和大小的信封。
EN: The post office sells envelopes of various types and sizes.
ZH: 我已将文件装进了一个大的信封。
EN: I have put the documents in a big envelope.
ZH: 这是一封你的朋友寄来的信，我刚刚从信封上看到了。
EN: This is a letter sent by your friend, I just saw it from the envelope.
ZH: 老师告诉我把论文放进一个透明的信封里。
EN: The teacher told me to put the essay in a transparent envelope.
ZH: 我今天需要去邮局买一些信封。
EN: I need to go to the post office today to buy some envelopes.
ZH: 请打印一些迷你尺寸的信封。
EN: Please print some mini-sized envelopes.
ZH: 这个信封上面有损坏的痕迹，我要换一个。
EN: This envelope has marks of damage on it, I want to exchange it.
ZH: 请确保把信封密封好以防止信件遗失。
EN: Please make sure to seal the envelope properly to prevent the letter from getting lost.
ZH: 他拆开了信封，仔细阅读了信内容。
EN: He opened the envelope and read the letter carefully.
ZH: 这个信封上附着了一张明信片。
EN: There is a postcard attached to this envelope.
